nodes.text: Doctor Aphra 14 is the fourteenth issue of the Marvel comic book series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra. The comic was written by Kieron Gillen with art by Kev Walker and released on November 15, 2017. The issue contains the story "Remastered Part I," in which Doctor Aphra is forced to work for the criminal syndicate controlled by Triple-Zero.
Doctor Aphra's antics are causing mayhem once again… But is she really the one calling the shots?
